               <msContents>
                  <summary>Image of Mary, መልክአ፡ ማርያም፡, Image of Jesus Christ, መልክአ፡  ኢየሱስ፡; Image of Saint George zä-Säläda Mogäs, መልክአ፡ ጊዮርጊስ፡ ዘሰሌዳ፡ ሞገስ።; Hymn to Saint George, “O who is quick for help,” ኦ፡ ፍጡነ፡ ረድኤት፡</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <locus from="1r" to="16v" facs="004">Fols 1r–16v</locus>
                     <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2891RepCh172">Malkǝʾa
                                                  Māryām</title>
                     <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i2">
                     <locus from="17r" to="32v" facs="020">Fols 17r–32v</locus>
                     <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2839RepCh123">Malkǝʾa
                                                  ʾIyasus</title>
                     <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i3"><locus from="33r" to="47r" facs="036">Fols 33r–47r</locus><title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2866RepCh147">Malkǝʾ-hymn to St
                                                  George</title><incipit xml:lang="gez">ሰላም፡ ለዝክረ፡ ስምከ፡ ዘሰሌዳ፡ ሞገስ፡ መጽሐፉ፡</incipit>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i4">
                     <locus from="47r" to="48r" facs="050">Fols 47r–48r</locus>
